## Hints for Future Agents
- The marker is ADK's BaseLlm.trackingHeaders; if ADK renames the header or
  drops the 'google-adk/' label the exclusion silently stops and ADK runs
  start showing duplicate usage. The test in this commit pins the behavior.
- User-supplied headers merge AFTER trackingHeaders, so a user could
  overwrite x-goog-api-client and re-enable wrapping inside ADK; not worth
  defending against.

